---
description: Enforce automated linting, formatting, and test checks for all code.
alwaysApply: true
globs: ["*.py"]
---
All code changes must adhere to automated linting, formatting, and test checks.
- Code should pass Black for formatting.
- Code should pass Flake8 or Ruff for linting.
- All existing tests must pass.
- Consider how these checks integrate into pre-commit hooks or CI.
